Class AffineCoordinateMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • iiv.data.AffineCoordinateMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoordinateMap, iiVScriptable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinearCoordinateMap, NiftiQFormCoordinateMap, NiftiSFormCoordinateMap

    public class AffineCoordinateMap
extends Object
implements CoordinateMap, iiVScriptable
    Class that converts coordinates into another space usually scanner-anatomical coordinates based on a affine transform.

    iiV1.182
    See Also:
